original_title: Dave Matthews Band - Austin City Limits
overview: Here’s Dave Matthews Band Austin City Limits setlist:  “Funny the Way It Is”  “Spaceman”  “Squirm”  “Lying in the Hands of God”  “Alligator Pie”  “Gravedigger”  “Why I Am”  “Seven”  “Lie in Our Graves”  “Shake Me Like a Monkey”  “Sister”  “You & Me”  “Jimi Thing”  “Time Bomb”  “Grey Street”  Possible encore: “Ants Marching”  Performances from the Austin City Limits taping will air on the show’s season premiere Oct. 3.
title: Dave Matthews Band - Austin City Limits
